These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pineapple, kiwi, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, filmmaking, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, surfing, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person eating lime##6
 5. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 8. the person eating pineapple is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
 9. the person eating asparagus is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
12. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
13. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | asparagus         | lime     | kiwi     | pineapple         |
| Hobby   | fishing | dancing    | filmmaking     | collecting |
| Sport   | biathlon       | lacrosse | weightlifting | surfing       |

