.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, hot-chocolate, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, paramedic, bartender, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, tennis, volleyball, parkour
 1. the bartender is not to the right of the chef##8
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person drinking cola is the paramedic##1
 5. the writer is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the right of the writer##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate          | lemonade      | cola      | mirinda   |
| Job        | bartender     | writer | paramedic | chef      |
| Sport      | parkour | tennis    | handball  | volleyball |

