.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, collecting, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, ambient, soul, house
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, boat, taxi
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 5. the person driving the ship is not the fan of disco##6
 6. the fan of disco is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the fan of disco is not to the right of the fan of house##8
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting  | gardening | woodworking | chess |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | disco      | house | soul        |
| Transport     | ship | boat       | taxi    | helicopter     |

