.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, adventure, scientific, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, trance, salsa, country
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, british, spanish
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the indonesian is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
 3. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the indonesian##8
 6. the british is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 7. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
 8. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
 9. the argentine is on the left of the british##1
10. the person watching musical movies is the british##1
11. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | musical | adventure    | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | trance     | ambient   | country     |
| Nationality   | argentine | british   | indonesian | spanish    |

