.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, filmmaking, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, time-travel, mystery, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, surfing, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking       | traveling | magic-tricks  | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | musical    | time-travel | action    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball   | surfing   | water-polo |

