.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, corn, spinach, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, spy, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, pakistani, british, japanese
 1. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
 2. the person watching musical movies is not the pakistani##6
 3. the british is somewhere between the person eating corn and the person watching musical movies##7
 4. the pakistani is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 6. the british is the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
 8. the japanese is between the person eating radish and the british##2
 9. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
10. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the person eating watermelon##8
11. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | corn      | spinach      | watermelon | radish |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | thriller    | musical | comedy     |
| Nationality   | indian    | british | japanese  | pakistani |

