 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person driving the subway is not the egyptian##6
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the right of the egyptian##8
 9. the egyptian is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
10. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
11. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the egyptian##8
12. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
13. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
