There 4 different types of food: nectarine, onion, strawberry, avocado
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, r&b, disco
1. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating avocado##5
2. the person eating nectarine is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the person eating strawberry##7
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
5. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
6. the person eating nectarine is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
7. the person eating avocado is the fan of folk##1
8. the person eating avocado is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person drinking milk##7
9. the person eating avocado is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
