.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, video-games, traveling
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, spanish, brazilian, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, roller, scooter
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 2. the mexican is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the brazilian##7
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 4. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the argentine is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
 7. the mexican is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 8. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
10. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
11. the argentine is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
13. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess    | video-games | traveling | rock-climbing    |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | mexican    | argentine      | spanish |
| Transport     | boat | quad-bike          | scooter      | roller       |

