The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, designer, entrepreneur, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, family, horror, time-travel
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 2. the entrepreneur is not the person drinking tea##6
 3. the writer is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 6. the person watching horror movies is the entrepreneur##1
 7. the designer is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
 8. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 9. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
10. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
11. the nurse is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | coffee  | hot-chocolate | tea |
| Job           | designer | entrepreneur | writer | nurse   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | horror  | family   | mystery   |

