.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, firefighter, scientist, fisherman
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, egyptian, canadian, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, scooter, skateboard, bike
 1. the indian is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
 2. the doctor is on the left of the indian##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the russian##3
 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the firefighter##1
 6. the scientist is on the right of the doctor##1
 7. the fisherman is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person driving the train is not the firefighter##6
 9. the fisherman is not to the left of the russian##8
10. the russian is not to the right of the firefighter##8
11. the scientist is somewhere between the russian and the person driving the train##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Job           | doctor  | scientist | firefighter | fisherman |
| Nationality   | canadian | indian           | russian  | egyptian |
| Transport     | train      | skateboard           | bike     | scooter  |

